# Hampirex – E-Commerce Data System

Hampirex is a large-scale e-commerce product management system built using WordPress and WooCommerce to manage and structure over 5000+ products.

## Overview
The project focuses on building a scalable product catalog system that handles product variations, categories, and structured data integration.

## Key Features
- Management of 5000+ product catalog
- Structured SKU and variation system
- Product data organization and mapping
- E-commerce platform optimization

## Technologies
- WordPress
- WooCommerce
- Data structuring and automation

## Impact
This project demonstrates large-scale product data management and real-world e-commerce infrastructure.

